f the job.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"faq-question-1693222861819\" class=\"rank-math-list-item\">\n<h3 class=\"rank-math-question \">Q3. Is graphic design a worthy career?<\/h3>\n<div class=\"rank-math-answer \">\n\n<p>Ans. If you want to do something creative, being a graphic designer lets you use your artistic skills in different ways. You could work from home, in an office, or even as a freelancer. As a graphic designer, you get to show your creativity and passion for art.<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Graphic Designer Salary Graphic design is all about creating visual art that communicates messages. This job is important in India and comes with different salaries. Graphic designers make logos, websites, and more to show what a company is like. This guide will help you understand how much money graphic designers can make in India and &#8230; <a title=\"Graphic Designer Salary In India\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/graphic-designer-salary\/\" aria-label=\"More on Graphic Designer Salary In India\">Read more<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":5202,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[35],"tags":[218],"class_list":["post-1270","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-web-development","tag-graphic-designer-salary","generate-columns","tablet-grid-50","mobile-grid-100","grid-parent","grid-33"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1270"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.skillvertex.com\/blog\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"h